<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <title>{{ title }}</title>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href=".././styles/forgot_password_page.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href=".././styles/colors.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
    <!-- Font Awesome -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <style>
        #form-forgot-password {
            padding: 5%;
            border: 2px solid gray;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            border-radius: 20px;
            margin: 10% auto;
            margin-left: 5%;
            margin-right: 5%;
            width: 50% auto;
            height: 100%;
        }

        div.row {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            width: 100%;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .col-1,
        .col-2 {
            width: 50%;
        }

        .col-2 img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
        }

        li:hover {
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        @media only screen and (max-width: 1024px) {

            .col-1,
            .col-2 {
                width: 100%;
                padding: 0;
                margin-top: 10%;
            }

            .col-2 img {
                width: 100%;
                height: auto;
                object-fit: cover;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <nav style="position: fixed; background-color: #1B76A1; width: 100%;" class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <a class="navbar-brand me-2" href="/about_us">
                <img src="../assets/logo.png" alt="MePass Logo" style="width: 5em; height: 2em;">
            </a>
        </div>
    </nav>
    <div id="container" style="padding: 2%; height: 100%;">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-1">
                <div id="form-forgot-password">
                    <h1 style="width: 80%;">Bạn quên<br> mật khẩu ?</h1>
                    <p style="margin-top: 4%; width: 80%;">Đừng lo, ai cũng gặp phải vấn đề này cả. Nhập email của bạn bên dưới để khôi phục mật khẩu.</p>
                    <h4 style="margin-top: 4%; width: 80%;">Email</h2>
                        <input class="input form-control" type="email" class="form-control" placeholder="Nhập email" style="width: 80%;">
                        <button id="btn_submit_email" class="btn btn-success" type="submit"
                            style="margin-top: 4%; background-color: #B0CBFA; width: 80%;">Quên mật khẩu</button>
                        <div class="line-with-text" style="width: 80%;">
                            <span>Hoặc</span>
                        </div>
                        <button onclick="window.location.href='/user/login/gg'" class="btn btn-success" style="background-color: #B0CBFA; width: 80%;">
                            <img src=".././assets/google_icon.png" alt="Google Icon"
                                style="width: 6%; height: auto; margin-right: 3%; " />
                            Đăng nhập với Google
                        </button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-2">
                <img src=".././assets/background_forgot_password.png" alt="Forgot password" class="img-fluid"
                    style="width: 70%; height: auto; ">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
<script src=".././scripts/forgotpasspage.js"></script>

</html>